<view class="login-page">
  <view class="grid-layer"></view>
  <view class="scan-line"></view>
  <view class="light light-a"></view>
  <view class="light light-b"></view>

  <view class="login-shell">
    <view class="brand-row">
      <view class="brand-mark">YBS</view>
      <view class="brand-copy">
        <text class="kicker">CLOUD ATTENDANCE OS</text>
        <text class="brand-name">优贝思校外托管中心</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="hero">
      <text class="hero-title">教师端登录</text>
      <text class="hero-sub">多设备同步 · 云端保存 · 管理员可追溯</text>
    </view>

    <view class="status-strip">
      <view class="status-item">
        <text class="status-dot"></text>
        <text>HTTPS 云端</text>
      </view>
      <view class="status-item right">
        <text>同步在线</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view class="form-panel">
      <view class="field">
        <text class="field-label">USERNAME</text>
        <input class="field-input" value="{{username}}" bindinput="onUsername" placeholder="输入账号" placeholder-class="placeholder" />
      </view>

      <view class="field">
        <text class="field-label">PIN</text>
        <input class="field-input" value="{{pin}}" bindinput="onPin" password type="number" placeholder="输入 PIN" placeholder-class="placeholder" />
      </view>

      <button class="login-button" loading="{{loading}}" bindtap="login">进入系统</button>
    </view>

    <view class="security-note">
      服务器地址已锁定为云端，普通使用时不可误改。每台手机独立登录，同步到同一套云端数据。
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
